import React, { useState } from 'react'; function EmpPostAJobPage() { const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ jobtitle: '', jobcategory: '', jobtype: '', offeredsalary: '', experience: '', qualification: '', gender: '', country: '', city: '', location: '', latitude: '', longitude: '', question: [], // Questions as an array of objects { question: '', options: [], correctAnswer: '' } email: '', website: '', estsince: '', completeaddress: '', description: '', startDate: '', endDate: '', Vacnices: '' }); const [error, setError] = useState(''); const [success, setSuccess] = useState(''); // Add a new question const addQuestion = () => { setFormData((prevData) => ({ ...prevData, question: [ ...prevData.question, { question: '', options: ['', '', '', ''], correctAnswer: '' } // Default question structure ] })); }; // Handle change for question text const handleQuestionChange = (e, index) => { const { value } = e.target; const updatedQuestions = [...formData.question]; updatedQuestions[index].question = value; setFormData((prevData) => ({ ...prevData, question: updatedQuestions })); }; // Handle change for options const handleOptionChange = (e, questionIndex, optionIndex) => { const { value } = e.target; const updatedQuestions = [...formData.question]; updatedQuestions[questionIndex].options[optionIndex] = value; setFormData((prevData) => ({ ...prevData, question: updatedQuestions })); }; // Handle change for correct answer const handleCorrectAnswerChange = (e, questionIndex) => { const { value } = e.target; const updatedQuestions = [...formData.question]; updatedQuestions[questionIndex].correctAnswer = value; setFormData((prevData) => ({ ...prevData, question: updatedQuestions })); }; // Handle form field changes const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setFormData((prevData) => ({ ...prevData, [name]: value })); }; // Handle form submission const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { const response = await fetch('http://localhost:8080/post-job', { method: 'POST', credentials: 'include', // Include cookies for session headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify(formData) }); const result = await response.json(); if (result.success) { setSuccess('Job posted successfully!'); setError(''); setFormData({ jobtitle: '', jobcategory: '', jobtype: '', offeredsalary: '', experience: '', qualification: '', gender: '', country: '', city: '', location: '', latitude: '', longitude: '', question: [], email: '', website: '', estsince: '', completeaddress: '', description: '', startDate: '', endDate: '', Vacnices: '' }); // Reset form data } else { setError(result.message || 'Failed to post the job.'); } } catch (error) { console.error('Error posting job:', error); setError('Error posting job, please try again.'); } };
